I"<p>Statistical/Machine learning models often depend on many <em>hyperparameters</em>, that define and control their learning capabilities. <!-- raw HTML omitted --><code>crossval</code><!-- raw HTML omitted --> is an R package that calculates these models' learning performances on given datasets, as a function of their hyperparameters.</p>
